    <Paragraph Code="ParagraphElement2"><![CDATA[<p>The demonstrated CheckedListBox has <em>DataSource</em> property set to 'Customer' table from the database.<br />The table defines 'CustomerID', 'ContactName' and other columns.<br />The <em>ValueMember </em>set to&nbsp;'CustomerID'&nbsp;and <em>DisplayMember</em>&nbsp;property set to 'ContactName'.<br />&nbsp;</p>]]></Paragraph>
